<ArticleLayout
  title="Pentagon's Tick Bioweapon Probe: A Denial With An Asterisk"
  description="In 2023, the Pentagon Inspector General investigated claims that the U.S. military weaponized ticks between 1950 and 1975 — and found nothing. The problem: the report also acknowledged it couldn't really look. This is the story of what it means when an official denial contains its own asterisk."
  category="Environmental Health"
